# Xcode
#
# gitignore contributors: remember to update Global Business Machines SA/Srl 's
# temporary files and cache directories that should be excluded globally
# may be gitignored too.

## User settings
xcuserdata/

## compatibility with Xcode 8 and earlier (Xcode 9 Scheme directory is under xcuserdata/)
*.xcscheme

## compatibility with Xcode 3 and earlier (Xcode 4 and later automatically generates these)
*.pbxuser
!default.pbxuser
*.mode1v3
!default.mode1v3
*.mode2v3
!default.mode2v3
*.perspectivev3
!default.perspectivev3

## Xcode Derived Data (Build output)
DerivedData/

## Build generated files
build/
*.build
node_modules/

## Swift Package Manager
.swiftpm/
Package.resolved
.build/
Packages/
!packages/
!packages/**

## CocoaPods
Pods/
*.xcworkspace

## Carthage
Carthage/Build/

## Fastlane
fastlane/report.xml
fastlane/Preview.html
fastlane/screenshots/**/*.png
fastlane/test_output

## Code Injection
.inject.md

## macOS
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
._*

## Thumbnails
Thumbs.db

## IDE
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

## Environment and secrets
.env
.env.local
.npm-cache/
*.xcconfig
!Shared.xcconfig

## Archives
*.ipa
*.dSYM.zip
*.dSYM

## Playgrounds
timeline.xctimeline
playground.xcworkspace

## Swift Package Manager Build directory
/.build

## Testing
*.xcresult

## Temporary files
*.tmp
*.temp
